3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a self-supervised approach to learning image features, which is a common theme in AI research. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper mentions the use of motion cues, which could be relevant to robotics applications. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with image segmentation, which is a common task in multimedia applications.
